(a^2+b^2)(c^2+d^2)=(ad-bc)^2+(ac+bd)^2
a^2+b^2=c^2
(3,4,5)
(5,12,13)
3^2+4^2=5^2
5^2+12^2=13^2
(3^2+4^2)(5^2+12^2)=(3 \cdot 12 - 4 \cdot 5)^2+(3 \cdot 5+4 \cdot 12)^2=5^2\cdot 13^2=4225
16^2+63^2=65^2
a_1^2 +b_1^2 = c_1^2
a_2^2 +b_2^2 = c_2^2
(a_1^2 +b_1^2)\cdot(a_2^2 +b_2^2)=(a_1\cdot b_2-a_2\cdot b_1)^2+(a_1\cdot a_2-b_1\cdot b_2)^2
a_1^2 +b_1^2 = c_1^2
(c_1^2)\cdot(c_2^2)=(a_1\cdot b_2-a_2\cdot b_1)^2+(a_1\cdot a_2-b_1\cdot b_2)^2
(c_1\cdot c_2)^2=(a_1\cdot b_2-a_2\cdot b_1)^2+(a_1\cdot a_2-b_1\cdot b_2)^2
